    {
      "type": "warmup",
      "content": "<h2>Warm-up (2-3 min)</h2>\n<p>Quick recall — key cmavo:</p>\n<pre><code>happy → ?       I observe → ?\npity → ?        I heard → ?\nhope → ?        In my opinion → ?\nagree → ?       Certainly → ?\n</code></pre>\n<p>(Answers: <code>.ui</code>, <code>za&#39;a</code>, <code>.uu</code>, <code>ti&#39;e</code>, <code>.a&#39;o</code>, <code>pe&#39;i</code>, <code>.ie</code>, <code>ju&#39;o</code>)</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "summary",
      "content": "<h2>Grammar Summary (3-4 min)</h2>\n<h3>Attitudinals (Emotions)</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Cmavo</th>\n<th>Emotion</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><code>.ui</code></td>\n<td>happiness</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.uinai</code></td>\n<td>unhappiness</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.uu</code></td>\n<td>pity</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.u&#39;i</code></td>\n<td>amusement</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.oi</code></td>\n<td>pain</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.a&#39;o</code></td>\n<td>hope</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.au</code></td>\n<td>desire</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.e&#39;e</code></td>\n<td>encouragement</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.ie</code></td>\n<td>agreement</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>.ienai</code></td>\n<td>disagreement</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Intensity Modifiers</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Modifier</th>\n<th>Level</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><code>cai</code></td>\n<td>extreme</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>sai</code></td>\n<td>strong</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>ru&#39;e</code></td>\n<td>weak</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>cu&#39;i</code></td>\n<td>neutral</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>nai</code></td>\n<td>opposite</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Evidentials (Knowledge Source)</h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Cmavo</th>\n<th>Source</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><code>ba&#39;a</code></td>\n<td>expectation</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>ti&#39;e</code></td>\n<td>hearsay</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>za&#39;a</code></td>\n<td>observation</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>pe&#39;i</code></td>\n<td>opinion</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>ju&#39;o</code></td>\n<td>certainty</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "other",
      "content": "<h2>Self-Test (5-6 min)</h2>\n<h3>Part A: Attitudinals (8 points)</h3>\n<p>What does each mean?</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>.ui</code> →</li>\n<li><code>.uu</code> →</li>\n<li><code>.a&#39;o</code> →</li>\n<li><code>.ie</code> →</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Add the right attitudinal:</p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>I&#39;m happy. → ?</li>\n<li>I feel pity. → ?</li>\n<li>I hope. → ?</li>\n<li>I agree. → ?</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li>happiness</li>\n<li>pity</li>\n<li>hope</li>\n<li>agreement</li>\n<li><code>.ui</code></li>\n<li><code>.uu</code></li>\n<li><code>.a&#39;o</code></li>\n<li><code>.ie</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>\n\n<h3>Part B: Intensity (4 points)</h3>\n<p>Modify <code>.ui</code> (happy):</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Very happy → ?</li>\n<li>Slightly happy → ?</li>\n<li>Unhappy (opposite) → ?</li>\n<li>Indifferent → ?</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li><code>.uisai</code></li>\n<li><code>.uiru&#39;e</code></li>\n<li><code>.uinai</code></li>\n<li><code>.uicu&#39;i</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>\n\n<h3>Part C: Evidentials (4 points)</h3>\n<p>Which evidential?</p>\n<ol>\n<li>I see it happening. → ?</li>\n<li>Someone told me. → ?</li>\n<li>In my opinion. → ?</li>\n<li>I&#39;m certain. → ?</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li><code>za&#39;a</code></li>\n<li><code>ti&#39;e</code></li>\n<li><code>pe&#39;i</code></li>\n<li><code>ju&#39;o</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>\n\n<h3>Part D: Combined (4 points)</h3>\n<p>Translate:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Happy! I heard you succeeded.</li>\n<li>I observe (pity) the dog is sick.</li>\n<li>Certainly, this is true.</li>\n<li>In my opinion (I agree), this is good.</li>\n</ol>\n<details>\n<summary>Answers</summary>\n\n<ol>\n<li><code>.ui ti&#39;e do snada</code></li>\n<li><code>za&#39;a .uu lo gerku cu bilma</code></li>\n<li><code>ju&#39;o ti jetnu</code></li>\n<li><code>pe&#39;i .ie ti xamgu</code></li>\n</ol>\n</details>"
    },
