      "type": "other",
      "content": "<h2>Integration Challenge (1-2 min)</h2>\n<h3>Tell an Emotional Story</h3>\n<p>Use at least:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Three different attitudinals</li>\n<li>Two evidentials</li>\n<li>One intensity modifier</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Example:</strong></p>\n<pre><code>ti&#39;e la .alis. pu snada .uisai\n.i za&#39;a .a&#39;o ri ba ze&#39;u gleki\n.i pe&#39;i .ie la .alis. cu drani\n.i .uicai mi tugni\n</code></pre>\n<p>(I heard Alice succeeded. Very happy! I observe, hope, she will be happy long-term. In my opinion, I agree, Alice is right. Ecstatic! I agree.)</p>\n<p>Create your own and say it aloud.</p>\n"
